OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fbright evening but some low cloud
OL,7,Fdeveloping along the east coast.
OL,8,FWidespread low cloud will feed in from
OL,9,Fthe east overnight with heavy showers
OL,10,Fdeveloping but staying dry and clearer
OL,11,Fin Southwest.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FA cloudy and cool day in the
OL,14,Feast with rain at times, possibly
OL,15,Fheavy at first. A little rain at first
OL,16,Fin the west then, bright, sunny and
OL,17,Fwarm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
